import React from 'react'

export const TodoAdd = () => {
  return (
    <form>
        <input
            type='text'
            placeholder = '¿Qué hay que hacer?'
            className='form-control'
        />
        <button 
            type='submit'
            className='btn btn-outline-primary mt-1'
        >Agregar
        </button>
    </form>
  )
}
